to build run make
	requires make & docker.io
	deb package will appear in directory with Makefile
	1st install with
		# apt-get install apt-transport-https && dpkg -i <package_name>
		# apt-get update && apt-get -f install
	upgrade:
		# dpkg -i <package_name>
		# apt-get update && apt-get -f install

to change to a new bitcore version
	change version in git checkout in satoshilabs-bitcore/Makefile
	create a new entry in satoshilabs-bitcore/debian/changelog
	then build as usual
